item.description:
I moved up the time on this meetup so that we do not run out of daylight in the woods.
I'll bring a flashlight just in case though.

We'll start the trail at 5:45 pm.

There is parking right behind the barn and a large field as well.

Adele wrote "It has a few walking trails which are very rarely frequented by anyone. One
of the trails leads out to a big field where the dogs can run around, play frisbee, etc."

Thanks to Adele & Bella for suggesting this location.
